      "role": "user",
      "content": "Hey, I'm studying for my Con Law exam and I'm a bit stuck. When it comes to the current Supreme Court's stance on the 2nd Amendment, do you think they're actually being faithful to what the Founders intended, or is this just a case of judicial overreach?",
